verbose_text: The expression of CYP1A2, CYP2C9, CYP2C19 and CYP2D6 in the cells grown on the MDS atelocollagen coat was elevated compared with that in the cells grown using conventional culture [3.3-fold (797.9 +/-73.0%), 1.4-fold (13.9 +/-0.9%), 1.4-fold (15.6 +/-0.8%), and 6.3-fold (9.6 +/-0.5%), respectively; XREF_FIG].
